{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Badges</h1>\n<h2>Demo</h2>\n<p><span class=\"c-badge c-badge--dark\">Dark Badge</span>\n<span class=\"c-badge c-badge--light\">light Badge</span>\n<span class=\"c-badge c-badge--outline-light\">light Badge</span>\n<span class=\"c-badge c-badge--dark u-bg-red\">Dark Badge (Red BG)</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"c-badge c-badge--dark\">Dark Badge</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"c-badge c-badge--dark u-font--semibold\">Dark Badge (Semibold)</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"c-badge c-badge--dark u-bg-red\">Dark Badge (Red BG)</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"c-badge c-badge--outline-light\">Outline Light Badge</span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>c-badge c-badge--dark<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Dark Badge<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>c-badge c-badge--light<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>light Badge<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</s